{"id": "1821", "post": "<div class=\"post-1821 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-buffalovps-com tag-chicago tag-openvz\" id=\"post-1821\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/buffalovps-6-75-1gb-openvz-vps-in-chicago/\" rel=\"bookmark\">BuffaloVPS \u2013 $6.75 1GB OpenVZ VPS in Chicago</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/buffalovps-com/\" rel=\"tag\">buffalovps.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/chicago/\" rel=\"tag\">chicago</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> May 19, 2011 @ 2:27 am, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://buffalovps.com/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/images/buffalovps.jpg\" class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"BuffaloVPS\"></a> Adam from <a href=\"http://buffalovps.com/\"><b>BuffaloVPS</b></a> emailed me their latest promo code for the LowEndBox readers. Similar to their <a href=\"/blog/buffalovps-6-99-1gb-openvz-vps-in-chicago/\">previous offer</a> but with slightly more discount. Use <b>prof</b> to get the \u201cProfessional\u201d plan for <b>$6.75/month</b>, and use <b>stan</b> to get the \u201cStandard\u201d plan for <b>$5.75/month</b>. Both discount are recurring. In the case of Professional plan that\u2019s roughly 55% off, and it has the following spec:</p><ul><li>1024MB memory</li><li>30GB storage</li><li>1500GB/month data transfer</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li></ul><p>You can <a href=\"https://billing.buffalovps.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=13&amp;promocode=prof\">use this link to sign up</a>, with the promo code pre-filled. Servers in Chicago (test IP: 205.234.203.74). Do note that they are reselling <a href=\"http://www.chicagovps.net/\">ChicagoVPS</a>\u2018s service (while waiting for their Buffalo data center to be completed). But then ChicagoVPS <a href=\"/blog/chicagovps-6-50-1024mb-openvz-vps-in-chicago/\">is promoting the very same \u201cProfessional\u201d package for $6.50/month</a> \u2014 just tested and the coupon code still works. I guess you can\u2019t go wrong with either, as both Adam (BuffaloVPS) and Chris (ChicagoVPS) have been quite helpful here.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fbuffalovps-6-75-1gb-openvz-vps-in-chicago%2F&amp;t=BuffaloVPS%20-%20%246.75%201GB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20Chicago\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=BuffaloVPS%20-%20%246.75%201GB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20Chicago&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fbuffalovps-6-75-1gb-openvz-vps-in-chicago%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flow